jokes.setup: Why do fathers take an extra pair of socks when they go golfing?
jokes.punchline: In case they get a hole in one!
Because they would crack each other up.

jokes.setup: I thought the dryer was shrinking my clothes.
jokes.punchline: Turns out it was the refrigerator all along.

jokes.setup: What did the ocean say to the beach?
Did you hear the rumor about butter?
jokes.punchline: Well, I'm not going to spread it!

jokes.setup: How many tickles does it take to make an octopus laugh?
